<P>The&s;e are the numbers of the fir&s;t tran&s;ver&s;e placed &s;lanting&mdash;, &s;o that there is not two in the &s;ame upright nor in the &s;ame tran&s;ver&s;e. I mu&s;t therefore di&s;po&s;e the numbers of the &s;econd tran&s;ver&s;e after the &s;ame manner, and be|cau&s;e that I mu&s;t avoid placing the fir&s;t number of this tran&s;ver&s;e, under the fir&s;t of the other, I cannot do better than to place it under the la&s;t in this manner.</P>
