<P>With the &s;ame Oeconomy I di&s;po&s;e the other tran&s;ver&s;es, placing always the fir&s;t number of the one under the la&s;t of the other; and for one of the diame|ters I put the middle tran&s;ver&s;e, becau&s;e that naturally it is Magical.</P>
